<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Specified_product_mim  Entity: product_identification  
   <express_ref linkend="specified_product:mim:Specified_product_mim.product_identification"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Specified_product_mim.product_identification">
A <b>product_identification</b> is a type of <b>configuration_item</b> and <b>characterized_object</b> that identifies a manufacturable product in a <b>product_class</b>.
</ext_description>
<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Specified_product_mim  Entity: product_identification  Attribute: item_concept 
   <express_ref linkend="specified_product:mim:Specified_product_mim.product_identification.item_concept"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Specified_product_mim.product_identification.item_concept">
The <b>product_class</b> the <b>product_identification</b> is a member of.
</ext_description>
<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Specified_product_mim  Entity: product_identification  Where: WR1 
   <express_ref linkend="specified_product:mim:Specified_product_mim.product_identification.wr:WR1"/>

  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Specified_product_mim.product_identification.wr:WR1">
Each <b>product_identification</b> shall be referenced as the configuration by 
at most one instance of <b>configuration_design</b> that references as design a 
<express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_formation"/>
which references as of_product a product which is contained in the of products set of a <b>product_related_product_category</b> with a name of either 'part', 'raw material', or 'tool'
</ext_description>
<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Specified_product_mim  Entity: product_identification  Where: WR2 
   <express_ref linkend="specified_product:mim:Specified_product_mim.product_identification.wr:WR2"/>

  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Specified_product_mim.product_identification.wr:WR2">
If the <b>product_identification</b> is of type <b>configurable_item</b>, it shall also be of type <b>product_specification</b>. If the <b>product_identification</b> is of type <b>product_specification</b>, it shall also be of type <b>configurable_item</b>. 
</ext_description>
<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Specified_product_mim  Entity: product_specification  
   <express_ref linkend="specified_product:mim:Specified_product_mim.product_specification"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Specified_product_mim.product_specification">
A <b>product_specification</b> is a type of <b>product_identification</b> and <b>configurable_item</b> that identifies a manufacturable product that is characterized with instances of <b>product_concept_feature</b>.
<p>The inherited attribute <b>item_concept_feature</b> points to a set of <b>product_concept_feature_association</b> instances that define the specified characteristics of the manufacturable product.</p>
</ext_description>
